WEBVTT

00:00:08.115 --> 00:00:10.785
(Lee Na Young)

00:00:16.525 --> 00:00:19.365
(Jung Eun Chae)

00:00:20.965 --> 00:00:23.705
(Lee Chung Ah)

00:00:31.105 --> 00:00:35.115
(Honour)

00:00:35.545 --> 00:00:39.485
(Supported by the Culture Ministry and Korea's Creative Content Agency)

00:00:40.685 --> 00:00:43.315
(All people, incidents, and backgrounds...)

00:00:43.385 --> 00:00:44.925
(in this drama are fictitious and unrelated to reality.)

00:00:44.985 --> 00:00:46.555
(Also, children and animals were filmed under production guidelines.)

00:00:55.535 --> 00:00:57.365
(Choi Ye Seul, Jo Yoo Jeong)

00:01:03.605 --> 00:01:05.505
I really need to see these jerks' faces.

00:01:05.875 --> 00:01:07.345
After doing something like this to kids,

00:01:07.545 --> 00:01:10.515
they pretend they're decent. They're not even human.

00:01:11.515 --> 00:01:14.815
Identifying the users is proving harder than we thought.

00:01:15.585 --> 00:01:18.285
Not a single name has come up. What about the police?

00:01:18.955 --> 00:01:20.695
How's the server trace coming along?

00:01:21.025 --> 00:01:23.025
As for the server location, Seung Jin...

00:01:23.325 --> 00:01:25.825
No. It seems even Detective Kim Seung Jin doesn't know,

00:01:26.125 --> 00:01:28.365
and it looks like the trace is going to take a while longer.

00:01:29.595 --> 00:01:32.935
We need to crack it to get the user list.

00:01:42.715 --> 00:01:45.715
You're not saying a word about who the users are.

00:01:46.615 --> 00:01:48.815
The arrest warrant for Park Je Yeol will be issued soon too.

00:01:49.155 --> 00:01:50.585
There's no point in you holding out like this.

00:01:51.125 --> 00:01:52.355
It won't do you any good.

00:01:56.555 --> 00:01:58.665
Prosecutor Park will be sacrificed, sure.

00:02:01.695 --> 00:02:02.695
But, Seon Kyu.

00:02:03.865 --> 00:02:06.935
Those people, the VIPs... They're different.

00:02:07.575 --> 00:02:09.735
You think they'll even bat an eye at this?

00:02:10.905 --> 00:02:11.905
No.

00:02:12.275 --> 00:02:15.375
They know it. They know they'll get away with it.

00:02:15.645 --> 00:02:20.385
Why? Because it has happened before, and they always get away clean.

00:02:23.625 --> 00:02:27.155
As for who those people are... I can't be the one to say.

00:02:29.995 --> 00:02:33.565
And you call yourself a detective, saying nonsense like that?

00:02:35.935 --> 00:02:36.935
So...

00:02:38.365 --> 00:02:41.035
is that why you went this far? To Hyun Jin, of all people?

00:02:42.035 --> 00:02:43.105
Look, man, I...

00:02:50.245 --> 00:02:54.555
I know at this point, what I did or didn't do doesn't mean a thing,

00:02:55.015 --> 00:02:56.585
but this part wasn't me.

00:03:00.895 --> 00:03:01.895
You guys...

00:03:02.195 --> 00:03:03.525
You really still don't get it, do you?

00:03:04.025 --> 00:03:05.025
Who was behind this.

00:03:07.665 --> 00:03:09.495
Are you doing okay staying with your parents?

00:03:11.165 --> 00:03:12.165
How's Sang A?

00:03:12.235 --> 00:03:13.505
(Episode 9)

00:03:15.735 --> 00:03:16.735
That's a relief.

00:03:17.775 --> 00:03:19.744
Tomorrow, we're going to file for divorce...

00:03:19.745 --> 00:03:21.715
the moment Park Je Yeol is arrested.

00:03:22.275 --> 00:03:24.985
And of course, you'll be able to get custody.

00:03:26.885 --> 00:03:29.985
Okay, I'll keep you updated on our progress.

00:03:36.095 --> 00:03:37.095
Min Seo? Are you asleep?

00:03:45.465 --> 00:03:48.105
- Yes. - Where are you? Are you home?

00:03:48.205 --> 00:03:49.805
- Yes. - What about Han Min Seo?

00:03:50.175 --> 00:03:51.305
Is she next to you?

00:03:51.545 --> 00:03:52.545
Min Seo?

00:03:53.445 --> 00:03:54.975
I think she's in her room. Why?

00:03:55.245 --> 00:03:56.345
Get out of there. Right now. Hurry.

00:03:56.615 --> 00:03:58.785
- Why? What's wrong? - The green hoodie...

00:03:59.385 --> 00:04:00.385
It's Han Min Seo.

00:04:02.185 --> 00:04:03.555
What are you talking about?

00:04:04.185 --> 00:04:07.155
I just talked to Seon Kyu. Detective Kim told him.

00:04:07.725 --> 00:04:10.495
You're in the same house as Lee Seon Hwa's killer right now.

00:04:12.695 --> 00:04:14.235
Hey, Yoon Ra Young, are you listening to me?

00:04:16.265 --> 00:04:18.235
Hey, Yoon Ra Young, answer me!

00:04:18.935 --> 00:04:19.935
Ra Young.

00:04:20.505 --> 00:04:21.675
Min Seo's gone.

00:04:23.175 --> 00:04:24.445
Hyun Jin, I'll call you right back.

00:04:44.225 --> 00:04:45.225
This is for you.

00:04:45.895 --> 00:04:47.435
(Lee Jun Hyeok)

00:04:49.795 --> 00:04:51.305
These are the candidates for the evaluation committee.

00:04:51.805 --> 00:04:54.075
Seven members will be selected for the final committee,

00:04:54.405 --> 00:04:55.805
but among them, the most influential candidates...

00:04:55.875 --> 00:04:59.405
who are basically locks are these four.

00:04:59.605 --> 00:05:00.645
(Lee Jong Jin)

00:05:00.715 --> 00:05:01.715
(Kang Wook Min)

00:05:03.785 --> 00:05:05.784
They have close ties to high-ranking officials...

00:05:05.785 --> 00:05:07.785
who have a vested interest in this project,

00:05:08.055 --> 00:05:10.885
so in this evaluation, they will back our competitor.

00:05:11.685 --> 00:05:13.025
If we can't get past them,

00:05:13.855 --> 00:05:15.695
we don't have a realistic chance of winning this bid.

00:05:18.265 --> 00:05:19.525
So that's why you chose Haeil, right?

00:05:20.095 --> 00:05:23.195
Because my mom has enough pull to reach them.

00:05:27.305 --> 00:05:30.005
How's the Connect case coming along?

00:05:31.275 --> 00:05:32.375
It's been tough.

00:05:33.275 --> 00:05:36.175
I doubt we'll make any progress until Park Je Yeol is investigated.

00:05:38.645 --> 00:05:39.945
That prosecutor will be dangerous.

00:05:40.385 --> 00:05:43.085
We think so too, and we're preparing for it.

00:05:43.825 --> 00:05:45.585
For whatever his last desperate move might be.

00:05:45.955 --> 00:05:48.195
No. I mean the prosecutor.

00:05:49.425 --> 00:05:52.295
Right now, he's the only one who knows who the users really are.

00:05:53.465 --> 00:05:57.305
The safest way to dispose of a bomb that's served its purpose...

00:05:57.365 --> 00:05:59.265
is to just go ahead and pull the pin.

00:06:04.145 --> 00:06:06.175
If there's anything I can do, just let me know.

00:06:08.175 --> 00:06:09.175
Thank you.

00:06:14.085 --> 00:06:15.185
Prosecutor Park Je Yeol.

00:06:15.715 --> 00:06:17.455
This is Detective Gu Seon Kyu from the Mujin Police Station.

00:06:25.125 --> 00:06:27.165
You think he might've already run off?

00:06:31.535 --> 00:06:35.075
Sir, I checked the CCTV. He was seen leaving two nights ago.

00:06:35.405 --> 00:06:37.505
- Put out an APB, now! - Yes, sir.

00:06:52.525 --> 00:06:54.055
(Storage Locker)

00:06:59.925 --> 00:07:02.335
(Storage Locker)

00:07:09.905 --> 00:07:10.905
Darn.

00:07:24.385 --> 00:07:25.425
It's me, Prosecutor Park.

00:07:26.925 --> 00:07:28.755
Why'd you bring the server into the country?

00:07:29.325 --> 00:07:31.065
To blackmail us with the evidence?

00:07:32.695 --> 00:07:35.695
How foolish can you be, Prosecutor Park?

00:07:37.435 --> 00:07:39.605
Do you really think you can handle making an enemy out of us?

00:07:41.335 --> 00:07:43.535
So you all get to just walk away from this,

00:07:44.145 --> 00:07:46.145
and I'm the one who takes the fall for all of this?

00:07:46.505 --> 00:07:49.015
I was under the impression that was the deal from the start.

00:07:50.315 --> 00:07:52.485
You think that's all I have on you?

00:07:53.185 --> 00:07:55.085
I was going to let it end here.

00:07:56.155 --> 00:07:57.425
Get this straight.

00:07:58.185 --> 00:07:59.685
You're the one who escalated this, not me.

00:08:11.665 --> 00:08:12.965
(CCTV in front of Dasam Station Exit 2)

00:08:15.575 --> 00:08:17.135
(Dashcam near Hansan-dong undeveloped area)

00:08:18.175 --> 00:08:20.975
There's only one possible explanation.

00:08:21.315 --> 00:08:23.945
She was a mole for Connect from the very beginning.

00:08:25.715 --> 00:08:29.815
But if that's true, why return Jun Hyeok's laptop to us?

00:08:30.215 --> 00:08:33.025
Detective Kim said the same thing. That they didn't order her to do it.

00:08:33.925 --> 00:08:35.495
He didn't seem like he was lying.

00:08:37.125 --> 00:08:38.365
None of this makes any sense.

00:08:38.965 --> 00:08:40.765
What could she have possibly wanted?

00:08:41.865 --> 00:08:45.305
Whatever her reasons, Han Min Seo attacked you both.

00:08:45.505 --> 00:08:47.035
And Hyun Jin could've been seriously hurt.

00:08:48.135 --> 00:08:50.034
Change your front door passcode now.

00:08:50.035 --> 00:08:52.275
If she contacts you, call the cops right away.

00:08:52.605 --> 00:08:53.745
And don't go soft on her.

00:08:56.475 --> 00:08:57.515
Hey, guys!

00:08:57.915 --> 00:08:59.644
The hacker responded!

00:08:59.645 --> 00:09:01.415
They'll hand over the laptop's decryption key.

00:09:02.485 --> 00:09:04.785
There was some information hardcoded in the code,

00:09:05.325 --> 00:09:07.085
and it was a username I recognised from a forum.

00:09:08.195 --> 00:09:12.665
He said he was just hired and wanted out, so I pressed him.

00:09:13.295 --> 00:09:14.295
Nice work.

00:09:19.605 --> 00:09:20.605
(Audio Transcripts)

00:09:23.435 --> 00:09:26.845
(Evidence Photos, Personal Info on Connect In, Timetable)

00:09:29.945 --> 00:09:30.945
(Connect In User List)

00:09:31.215 --> 00:09:32.445
A user list?

00:09:34.815 --> 00:09:36.315
(Yeo Min Seok, Minister of Future Strategy)

00:09:36.385 --> 00:09:37.625
(Choi Sik Yeong, Assembly Member)

00:09:40.795 --> 00:09:43.755
A scandal that could rock the entire country.

00:09:44.165 --> 00:09:45.195
(Yoon Dae Hyeon, Seoul City Director)

00:09:45.265 --> 00:09:46.265
(Ryu Seung Beom, Daily Baejin CEO)

00:09:46.765 --> 00:09:48.095
So this is why.

00:09:48.735 --> 00:09:50.035
This is why they killed Jun Hyeok.

00:09:50.535 --> 00:09:52.905
This isn't just a list of johns.

00:09:54.605 --> 00:09:56.605
Legal, political, and media circles.

00:09:57.035 --> 00:09:59.205
They're all apex predators in their respective fields.

00:09:59.605 --> 00:10:01.915
They can all act as shields for one another.

00:10:02.345 --> 00:10:04.845
Exactly. This is a cartel.

00:10:05.685 --> 00:10:09.085
If one of them gets into trouble, another shuts down the press,

00:10:09.155 --> 00:10:10.785
and someone else obstructs the investigation.

00:10:11.255 --> 00:10:14.825
A cartel bound together by their depraved desires.

00:10:19.225 --> 00:10:20.495
Is this...

00:10:21.295 --> 00:10:22.695
the Connect In server?

00:10:24.605 --> 00:10:26.105
We don't have to worry about this, do we?

00:10:26.935 --> 00:10:29.875
Because all the evidence against us that was stored here is gone.

00:10:30.275 --> 00:10:34.815
If this fuss drags on, we have members recruited for this.

00:10:35.115 --> 00:10:38.915
We'll throw a few to the wolves, and things will die down.

00:10:39.315 --> 00:10:40.315
All right, good.

00:10:42.055 --> 00:10:45.185
I've got enough on my plate with the National Assembly Audit.

00:10:45.355 --> 00:10:47.425
Wasting my energy on something so trivial...

00:10:47.755 --> 00:10:48.995
It's just so aggravating.

00:10:49.325 --> 00:10:51.625
What, you think you're the only one going through this audit?

00:10:52.725 --> 00:10:55.735
Hey, that's what I'm saying. So cut me some slack.

00:10:56.295 --> 00:11:01.105
He's different after hours. He's got a sharp tongue on him.

00:11:03.805 --> 00:11:06.875
So, how are we handling Prosecutor Park?

00:11:09.445 --> 00:11:10.445
First off,

00:11:11.015 --> 00:11:13.085
since public opinion is a factor in the first trial,

00:11:13.645 --> 00:11:18.425
how about 15 years, for appearances? He's also up for soliciting murder.

00:11:18.625 --> 00:11:20.025
But if the sentence is too long,

00:11:20.385 --> 00:11:24.525
that might cause an uproar. Seven years sounds about right.

00:11:24.695 --> 00:11:26.465
We can whittle it down during the appeals.

00:11:26.995 --> 00:11:30.765
- That works. The optics aren't bad. - Okay, right.

00:11:30.835 --> 00:11:33.435
- Then I'll pass the message along. - Okay.

00:11:35.175 --> 00:11:39.405
Okay, next time we pick an agent, we must vet their background better.

00:11:39.805 --> 00:11:41.675
You want someone who's already in on the game.

00:11:41.775 --> 00:11:44.815
I thought this educated type would be different, but...

00:11:45.315 --> 00:11:47.385
- I should've known. - Exactly.

00:11:47.755 --> 00:11:51.325
Gosh, I'm starting to get restless.

00:11:51.385 --> 00:11:54.695
We should lay low until Park's arrest, don't you think?

00:11:56.755 --> 00:11:57.795
What's there to be afraid of?

00:11:58.225 --> 00:11:59.395
Is this your first time at the rodeo?

00:11:59.665 --> 00:12:02.835
- Haeil will tie up the loose ends. - Of course.

00:12:03.795 --> 00:12:05.305
- Let's have a drink. - Let's.

00:12:05.365 --> 00:12:06.465
- Cheers. - Let's have a drink.

00:12:07.505 --> 00:12:10.805
You all worked hard. What a relief. Like getting a rotten tooth pulled.

00:12:18.785 --> 00:12:20.715
- Madam Chairman. - Hey.

00:12:26.155 --> 00:12:27.325
Thank you for coming.

00:12:28.055 --> 00:12:29.055
Of course.

00:12:30.455 --> 00:12:31.695
Your plan for Shin Jae...

00:12:32.425 --> 00:12:35.465
to give her a way to escape Haeil...

00:12:36.535 --> 00:12:37.765
Have you changed your mind about that?

00:12:39.005 --> 00:12:40.505
No, I have not.

00:12:43.235 --> 00:12:44.245
In that case,

00:12:44.805 --> 00:12:46.105
this is my business with you.

00:12:49.645 --> 00:12:50.945
(The Prime Smart City Legal Retainer Agreement)

00:12:59.125 --> 00:13:01.055
Are you terminating the retainer agreement?

00:13:03.895 --> 00:13:06.395
I'm sure you know exactly what this means.

00:13:08.565 --> 00:13:09.965
The Minister of Future Strategy,

00:13:10.395 --> 00:13:12.205
the Chairman of the Ruling Party Urban Committee,

00:13:13.135 --> 00:13:14.165
and the Mayor of Mujin.

00:13:14.735 --> 00:13:17.305
The most crucial players for the Smart City bid.

00:13:18.205 --> 00:13:21.645
You'd give up connections you need to sway the evaluation committee.

00:13:22.345 --> 00:13:23.415
And that's not all.

00:13:23.945 --> 00:13:27.855
I will use every resource I have to stop The Prime's bid.

00:13:28.955 --> 00:13:31.755
And you of all people should know...

00:13:32.855 --> 00:13:34.025
that I have the power to do it.

00:13:35.425 --> 00:13:36.825
If that's what you want, then go right ahead.

00:13:38.295 --> 00:13:39.295
However,

00:13:40.765 --> 00:13:41.995
by the day of the bid,

00:13:42.895 --> 00:13:44.565
do you really think your connections will still exist?

00:13:53.975 --> 00:13:56.915
I'm a firm believer that justice will prevail, Madam Chairman.

00:13:58.415 --> 00:13:59.545
Thank you for the tea.

00:14:12.925 --> 00:14:16.335
Here's the background check you requested on Baek Tae Joo.

00:14:16.435 --> 00:14:17.535
How deep did you go?

00:14:17.735 --> 00:14:21.805
Level A. Meaning we used all our intelligence networks.

00:14:23.635 --> 00:14:28.245
We investigated in Korea and the US legal, financial, and real estate.

00:14:28.675 --> 00:14:31.385
We have his finance and legal records...

00:14:31.615 --> 00:14:33.385
from school days to the present.

00:14:33.715 --> 00:14:36.655
Interviews with his associates, his health and medical records,

00:14:37.085 --> 00:14:38.785
down to his private life, scandals, and all the back-alley rumours.

00:14:39.285 --> 00:14:40.285
Good work.

00:14:42.325 --> 00:14:43.325
(Baek Tae Joo: Smart City)

00:14:43.395 --> 00:14:44.395
(The story from those close to him)

00:14:45.495 --> 00:14:46.495
("High School Student Baek Tae Joo,")

00:14:46.565 --> 00:14:47.565
("Funding Sick Kids' Care")

00:14:53.335 --> 00:14:54.405
("2006 Seo Ji Yoon Case: Her Tragic Death")

00:14:54.475 --> 00:14:56.275
("The Powerful Figures on the Vanished 'Seo Ji Yoon List'")

00:14:59.645 --> 00:15:01.915
(Haeil Law Firm, 2006)

00:15:05.015 --> 00:15:06.285
What do you mean, a call log?

00:15:06.885 --> 00:15:08.185
There was no such evidence.

00:15:08.385 --> 00:15:11.525
There was a tip. It's already been sent to the prosecution.

00:15:11.885 --> 00:15:13.724
It has our top clients' names.

00:15:13.725 --> 00:15:15.395
They're already calling it the Seo Ji Yoon List.

00:15:16.125 --> 00:15:17.625
For us, this is the worst kind of evidence.

00:15:20.595 --> 00:15:22.695
Then we just have to make it disappear.

00:15:23.535 --> 00:15:25.035
Make it as if it never existed.

00:15:26.435 --> 00:15:28.005
- How? - Go...

00:15:28.435 --> 00:15:30.575
and tell all those big shots on the list.

00:15:32.405 --> 00:15:35.375
That they now owe us a huge favour.

00:15:40.485 --> 00:15:42.415
("An Actress's Tragic Death, How Did the Call Logs Vanish?")

00:15:42.485 --> 00:15:43.485
(The identity of the mysterious hacker)

00:15:55.865 --> 00:15:58.265
(Haeil Law Firm)

00:16:05.975 --> 00:16:07.275
Hello, ma'am.

00:16:13.085 --> 00:16:14.085
(CEO's Office)

00:16:18.385 --> 00:16:21.055
What are you doing here, waltzing into this office?

00:16:28.295 --> 00:16:31.605
If you don't like it here, you're always free to leave.

00:16:34.235 --> 00:16:35.505
(Letter of resignation)

00:16:36.105 --> 00:16:39.305
You're the one who must sign this and clear out of this office.

00:16:41.515 --> 00:16:42.775
You've got some nerve.

00:16:43.345 --> 00:16:45.215
I'm speaking for every employee at LnJ.

00:16:45.715 --> 00:16:49.315
We cannot accept a Connect In user as our leader.

00:16:52.725 --> 00:16:53.755
Is that so?

00:16:54.355 --> 00:16:55.995
I have no idea what you're talking about.

00:16:56.655 --> 00:16:58.765
I have never been involved in any kind of scandal.

00:16:59.795 --> 00:17:02.195
These are all just your baseless accusations.

00:17:03.595 --> 00:17:04.765
Is that all you have to say?

00:17:05.635 --> 00:17:06.865
Then here's our response.

00:17:10.435 --> 00:17:12.775
(LnJ attorneys hold press conference releasing the "Connect In" list)

00:17:15.345 --> 00:17:19.215
We are here today to name the high-ranking officials...

00:17:19.415 --> 00:17:22.055
involved in the Connect In sexual exploitation crimes.

00:17:24.755 --> 00:17:28.495
The names of the perpetrators are as follows.

00:17:30.995 --> 00:17:32.164
- Goodness! - Unbelievable!

00:17:32.165 --> 00:17:34.294
We see the name of the Minister of Future Strategy.

00:17:34.295 --> 00:17:35.295
Is that correct?

00:17:35.365 --> 00:17:38.035
Most are high-ranking figures from politics, business, and law.

00:17:38.105 --> 00:17:39.505
Do you have concrete evidence to back this up?

00:17:39.565 --> 00:17:40.905
Are you saying there are more users than this?

00:17:40.965 --> 00:17:43.975
- Is law enforcement aware of this? - Are you saying this is true?

00:17:44.035 --> 00:17:46.105
- Is there an additional list? - Are you sure about this?

00:17:46.175 --> 00:17:49.345
- Is all of this credible? - Do you have proof that it's true?

00:17:49.415 --> 00:17:53.115
The perpetrators named are those who, by victim testimony,

00:17:53.185 --> 00:17:55.485
were confirmed to have sexually exploited them.

00:18:01.595 --> 00:18:02.595
I'm sorry.

00:18:03.225 --> 00:18:04.255
I can't look at them.

00:18:05.425 --> 00:18:06.425
The look in his eyes...

00:18:06.965 --> 00:18:08.835
is exactly the same as it was that day.

00:18:09.665 --> 00:18:10.935
Is this the guy?

00:18:11.605 --> 00:18:15.035
Yes. I met him at around 10:30pm.

00:18:15.605 --> 00:18:17.135
That's him.

00:18:19.345 --> 00:18:21.645
I'm sure of it. Down to the scar on his chin.

00:18:22.075 --> 00:18:25.245
His wallet. He had a National Assembly ID in it.

00:18:26.085 --> 00:18:27.985
On behalf of the victims,

00:18:28.055 --> 00:18:31.255
we will file criminal complaints against these perpetrators.

00:18:31.525 --> 00:18:35.195
Does the list you released today include every Connect In user?

00:18:35.395 --> 00:18:40.065
Today's defendants are on a list of perpetrators we have obtained.

00:18:40.695 --> 00:18:44.165
The rest will be submitted to police for their investigation.

00:18:44.235 --> 00:18:47.465
And we will take further action based on their findings.

00:18:47.535 --> 00:18:49.135
So how many more perpetrators are there?

00:18:53.075 --> 00:18:57.415
I want to stress that this is not simply a case about prostitution.

00:18:57.615 --> 00:18:59.485
But a crime of sexual exploitation.

00:18:59.815 --> 00:19:03.215
Victims were forced into prostitution.

00:19:03.455 --> 00:19:08.255
And they knowingly condoned it while abusing and assaulting them.

00:19:08.725 --> 00:19:12.825
We won't rest until everyone involved in this crime...

00:19:13.295 --> 00:19:15.065
is brought to justice.

00:19:21.605 --> 00:19:24.005
Among the victims we represent...

00:19:24.645 --> 00:19:26.375
is one of the girls who dealt with you.

00:19:28.315 --> 00:19:29.445
We'll see you in court.

00:19:32.745 --> 00:19:33.745
(Letter of resignation)

00:20:04.945 --> 00:20:07.185
So you've really gone and caused this disaster.

00:20:09.415 --> 00:20:10.685
Just brilliant, all of you.

00:20:12.125 --> 00:20:14.855
Causing all this trouble again because you had no self-control.

00:20:17.495 --> 00:20:20.295
Seo Ji Yoon's list from 20 years ago.

00:20:21.665 --> 00:20:24.765
If it weren't for that, Haeil wouldn't be what it is today.

00:20:27.165 --> 00:20:30.535
Have you really learned nothing from what happened back then?

00:20:30.835 --> 00:20:33.145
They were all terrified their names would get out,

00:20:33.445 --> 00:20:35.615
and since I was the one who got my hands dirty to fix it,

00:20:36.715 --> 00:20:39.445
you'd think they would've learned to clean up after themselves.

00:20:40.245 --> 00:20:41.245
And you.

00:20:41.715 --> 00:20:44.185
When did you start playing with fire with them?

00:20:44.685 --> 00:20:48.255
When I put you with them, it was to clean things up,

00:20:48.355 --> 00:20:50.455
not to roll around in the mud with them.

00:20:59.505 --> 00:21:02.235
This is the user list that was submitted to the police.

00:21:04.775 --> 00:21:07.875
Some of the names on that list are on this one too.

00:21:08.375 --> 00:21:13.045
If we let this go, Seo Ji Yoon's list might surface again.

00:21:15.555 --> 00:21:17.385
And people will start to wonder.

00:21:17.915 --> 00:21:21.355
They'll wonder how the key evidence, Seo Ji Yoon's call logs,

00:21:22.025 --> 00:21:24.655
ended up disappearing from the prosecutor's office.

00:21:33.705 --> 00:21:37.175
Jung Hyeon. You need to decide where you stand.

00:21:37.475 --> 00:21:40.075
If you're here to threaten me, then stop being so pathetic.

00:21:40.675 --> 00:21:42.145
And if you're here to ask for my help,

00:21:42.775 --> 00:21:44.645
then you need to drop the attitude.

00:21:50.155 --> 00:21:52.085
I'm merely expressing my concern.

00:21:53.325 --> 00:21:54.755
If things get serious for them,

00:21:55.825 --> 00:21:58.925
where will Haeil find shelter from the storm?

00:22:05.005 --> 00:22:07.765
For now, come back to Haeil.

00:22:25.585 --> 00:22:26.585
(Haeil Law Firm)

00:22:32.225 --> 00:22:34.025
The Minister of Future Strategy...

00:22:35.795 --> 00:22:37.935
The Chairman of the Ruling Party Urban Committee...

00:22:38.905 --> 00:22:40.735
The Mayor of Mujin...

00:22:41.435 --> 00:22:42.935
The Minister of Future Strategy,

00:22:43.075 --> 00:22:45.045
the Chairman of the Ruling Party Urban Committee,

00:22:45.145 --> 00:22:46.205
and the Mayor of Mujin.

00:22:46.505 --> 00:22:49.115
The most crucial players for the Smart City bid.

00:22:49.675 --> 00:22:51.945
You'd give up connections you need...

00:22:52.615 --> 00:22:54.045
to sway the evaluation committee.

00:22:55.115 --> 00:22:56.155
However,

00:22:57.215 --> 00:22:58.354
by the day of the bid,

00:22:58.355 --> 00:23:00.125
do you really think your connections will still exist?

00:23:03.295 --> 00:23:07.365
(CEO Seong Tae Im)

00:23:23.175 --> 00:23:24.675
(Call records)

00:23:25.285 --> 00:23:28.455
(Call records)

00:23:30.155 --> 00:23:32.785
(Call records)

00:23:35.095 --> 00:23:38.195
I'm a firm believer that justice will prevail, Madam Chairman.

00:24:10.125 --> 00:24:11.125
Yes?

00:24:16.795 --> 00:24:19.335
Attorney Yoon?

00:24:20.235 --> 00:24:21.235
Su Eun?

00:24:25.575 --> 00:24:28.815
- Isn't she a little plain? - You're too young to get it.

00:24:29.275 --> 00:24:31.175
If you wanted someone more seasoned,

00:24:31.745 --> 00:24:33.245
you should've gone to Gangnam.

00:24:34.285 --> 00:24:37.655
Same old story. It gets old.

00:24:38.525 --> 00:24:41.125
See? This is what they're like at that age.

00:24:46.195 --> 00:24:47.465
There was this one day...

00:24:49.895 --> 00:24:52.165
when things were so awful I just wanted to die.

00:24:53.005 --> 00:24:54.265
And I thought if I died,

00:24:55.135 --> 00:24:57.135
at least people would find out...

00:24:57.735 --> 00:25:00.005
the reason why.

00:25:02.315 --> 00:25:03.915
So I made these recordings.

00:25:05.685 --> 00:25:07.615
I should have given this to you sooner.

00:25:08.285 --> 00:25:09.285
I'm so sorry.

00:25:11.055 --> 00:25:14.085
Su Eun, you have nothing to be sorry for.

00:25:17.125 --> 00:25:20.425
I understand. By having me listen to this,

00:25:21.065 --> 00:25:22.065
Su Eun,

00:25:22.735 --> 00:25:26.435
you had to relive that painful moment all over again.

00:25:28.065 --> 00:25:29.775
Even if you did it for my sake.

00:25:36.515 --> 00:25:40.185
No one has the right to know how you were hurt,

00:25:40.445 --> 00:25:42.385
the specifics of it, or how much you suffered.

00:25:42.885 --> 00:25:45.285
If making this public causes you pain,

00:25:45.955 --> 00:25:46.955
then...

00:25:47.285 --> 00:25:49.695
this would all be pointless, wouldn't it?

00:25:52.595 --> 00:25:55.035
That's why, even if I'd gotten this before the press conference,

00:25:55.295 --> 00:25:57.595
I never would have released it.

00:26:00.335 --> 00:26:03.705
Shouldn't we use it for the trial, though?

00:26:04.805 --> 00:26:05.845
As evidence.

00:26:07.545 --> 00:26:11.885
We'll follow proper procedure to ensure it never gets leaked.

00:26:18.525 --> 00:26:19.755
Thank you.

00:26:37.335 --> 00:26:38.945
I gave you a clear warning.

00:26:39.775 --> 00:26:41.175
You brought this on yourselves.

00:26:52.585 --> 00:26:53.585
Sang A.

00:26:57.925 --> 00:27:01.325
Sang A. I'm getting out of here.

00:27:01.995 --> 00:27:04.235
Come with me, okay?

00:27:05.935 --> 00:27:06.935
Why?

00:27:07.405 --> 00:27:08.605
Are you worried it might be dangerous?

00:27:09.135 --> 00:27:10.805
I saw it all on the news.

00:27:12.345 --> 00:27:14.275
How could you do something like that?

00:27:14.805 --> 00:27:15.815
Sang A.

00:27:16.245 --> 00:27:19.445
- You're misunderstanding. - To think that you're my dad...

00:27:20.045 --> 00:27:21.445
is just horrifying.

00:27:26.485 --> 00:27:28.055
After everything I've done for you!

00:27:30.495 --> 00:27:32.225
You're just like your mother.

00:27:33.095 --> 00:27:35.535
Ungrateful and completely selfish.

00:27:37.265 --> 00:27:39.065
You don't care what happens to me,

00:27:39.435 --> 00:27:42.305
as long as you two get away with it, is that it?

00:27:43.935 --> 00:27:45.605
Don't ever come looking for me again.

00:27:46.775 --> 00:27:49.875
Sang A!

00:27:51.515 --> 00:27:52.515
Sang A!

00:28:05.225 --> 00:28:08.665
What on earth? Let go of me, you jerks!

00:28:09.765 --> 00:28:10.765
Let go!

00:28:25.745 --> 00:28:27.515
Min Seo, I'm here.

00:28:33.855 --> 00:28:36.755
There's only one possible explanation.

00:28:37.525 --> 00:28:40.265
She was a mole for Connect from the very beginning.

00:29:50.365 --> 00:29:53.765
I want to hear from you directly why you did it.

00:30:17.755 --> 00:30:18.795
I...

00:30:19.465 --> 00:30:21.495
have never seen my dad...

00:30:22.695 --> 00:30:23.965
act like that before.

00:30:26.365 --> 00:30:29.235
So you resent your dad too?

00:30:30.935 --> 00:30:32.175
I don't know.

00:30:34.145 --> 00:30:35.205
I was just...

00:30:36.145 --> 00:30:37.915
so scared.

00:30:42.185 --> 00:30:45.755
Should I tell the police? That my dad came to see me.

00:30:47.055 --> 00:30:48.055
No.

00:30:48.855 --> 00:30:49.855
Don't.

00:30:51.525 --> 00:30:53.095
Then what should I do?

00:30:53.995 --> 00:30:55.535
He has to pay for what he's done.

00:30:58.865 --> 00:31:01.205
Not you. Your dad.

00:31:02.205 --> 00:31:04.405
- This is LnJ Law Firm. - Did the fax come in?

00:31:04.475 --> 00:31:07.745
Can you give me a hand with this when you're done? They keep coming.

00:31:07.875 --> 00:31:10.645
- We just heard from the legal team. - Yes, I'm aware.

00:31:11.175 --> 00:31:13.485
Looks like they're making a move.

00:31:13.615 --> 00:31:15.285
"Groundless," "false statements."

00:31:15.415 --> 00:31:20.085
- "Defamation," "Libel." - "Motion for a publication ban."

00:31:20.255 --> 00:31:24.555
So predictable. Seriously. I've seen this a thousand times.

00:31:24.625 --> 00:31:29.235
Their next move is obvious too, but the problem is it always works.

00:31:29.265 --> 00:31:33.235
You need to keep your strength up. These are a rare treat.

00:31:33.405 --> 00:31:35.605
Have one, everyone. Let's get our strength back.

00:31:38.075 --> 00:31:39.445
Thank you.

00:31:50.515 --> 00:31:54.355
They want a fight, they'll get one. They think they'll get away with it,

00:31:54.425 --> 00:31:58.225
but we're not exactly pushovers ourselves.

00:32:00.195 --> 00:32:02.835
So they think they can tie our hands like this?

00:32:03.795 --> 00:32:05.564
The firms that sent these notices.

00:32:05.565 --> 00:32:07.634
Pull up a list of all their publicly traded clients...

00:32:07.635 --> 00:32:08.905
