Hyundai Bank, Mujin Airlines, right?

00:32:16.315 --> 00:32:19.115
Their legal counsel is Yakcheon Law Firm.

00:32:20.545 --> 00:32:23.485
One perpetrator in the Connect In case just retained Yakcheon.

