- Due to the Connect case... - Isn't a joint HQ better for us...

00:35:49.255 --> 00:35:51.725
than the prosecutors working alone?

00:35:51.755 --> 00:35:53.895
Will the investigation speed up after a joint HQ is formed?

00:35:53.925 --> 00:35:56.235
- It was my mom. - The expectations are rising.

00:35:56.295 --> 00:35:58.765
Every single person they just named owes my mother.

00:35:59.705 --> 00:36:01.964
Among those newly assigned to headquarters...

00:36:01.965 --> 00:36:04.005
is Prosecutor Kim Jung Woo of Seoul Southern Office...

00:36:04.775 --> 00:36:06.075
So my mother's making her move.

00:36:06.105 --> 00:36:09.444
He was a key member of the task force...

00:36:09.445 --> 00:36:11.745
that took down a major drug distributor...

00:36:14.045 --> 00:36:15.115
Start with the office.

00:36:16.285 --> 00:36:19.555
- The office. - Wait a minute. What is all this?

00:36:19.955 --> 00:36:21.055
Hey, hold on!

00:36:25.765 --> 00:36:27.694
What do you think you're doing?

00:36:27.695 --> 00:36:30.835
You're Attorney Kang Shin Jae, CEO of the LnJ law firm, correct?

00:36:31.535 --> 00:36:32.905
We're from the Joint Investigation HQ.

00:36:34.805 --> 00:36:37.104
You're under suspicion for obstructing justice...

00:36:37.105 --> 00:36:39.405
and illegally obtaining evidence against Park Je Yeol.

00:36:39.545 --> 00:36:41.744
We'll now begin a search and seizure...

00:36:41.745 --> 00:36:43.945
- of all the evidence in this case. - You can't go in there.

00:36:46.115 --> 00:36:47.115
Sir.

00:36:54.155 --> 00:36:55.824
Should we force our way in?

00:36:55.825 --> 00:36:58.625
You know this is obstructing justice, right?

00:37:21.215 --> 00:37:23.155
Let's move!

00:37:35.735 --> 00:37:37.635
(Police)

00:37:39.935 --> 00:37:41.065
Mujin Police Public Services desk. How can I...

00:37:43.735 --> 00:37:44.735
What brings you here?

00:37:44.736 --> 00:37:46.775
I came to talk about the Joint Investigation HQ,

00:37:47.345 --> 00:37:48.445
but what's all this?

00:37:48.745 --> 00:37:52.245
It's nothing. I was put on standby, so they just have me here for now.

00:37:52.315 --> 00:37:54.644
- Once the internal audit is over... - Right.

00:37:54.645 --> 00:37:57.054
An internal audit? They pulled you off the case...

00:37:57.055 --> 00:37:58.515
and stuck you here as retaliation.

00:37:58.915 --> 00:38:01.155
Calm down. Getting worked up is bad for you.

00:38:01.225 --> 00:38:02.795
Let's go. We can talk outside.

00:38:09.165 --> 00:38:10.165
What do you think you're doing?

00:38:12.465 --> 00:38:17.005
Sit down. I had some porridge made for you to soothe your stomach.

00:38:17.075 --> 00:38:18.075
The Joint Investigation HQ.

00:38:18.805 --> 00:38:20.075
I know you're behind this, Mom.

00:38:23.345 --> 00:38:24.515
You should have seen it coming.

00:38:25.045 --> 00:38:28.185
You were just circling the case without any hard evidence.

00:38:28.345 --> 00:38:31.855
Didn't it occur to you that the tables could be turned?

00:38:32.215 --> 00:38:36.055
Who would've thought my own mother would be pushing me to the edge?

00:38:37.195 --> 00:38:40.925
We've never been on the same side, but this is different.

00:38:41.125 --> 00:38:42.935
Mom, you targeted me.

00:38:43.995 --> 00:38:45.865
Why would you go this far?

00:38:46.865 --> 00:38:50.805
I just did what I've always done.

00:38:51.635 --> 00:38:53.345
What I know how to do.

00:38:53.475 --> 00:38:56.345
For Haeil? For your clients?

00:38:58.215 --> 00:38:59.215
That's right.

00:39:01.985 --> 00:39:04.315
Then I guess I'll just do what I've always done.

00:39:06.125 --> 00:39:07.285
What I have to do.

00:39:13.695 --> 00:39:16.465
Thank you for proving that I was right, Mom.

00:39:17.695 --> 00:39:19.405
Haeil must be eradicated from this country.

00:39:23.335 --> 00:39:24.705
Be careful of Baek Tae Joo.

00:39:25.305 --> 00:39:27.475
He has us both you and me...

00:39:28.205 --> 00:39:30.275
in the palm of his hand.

00:39:31.945 --> 00:39:34.445
What is that supposed to mean?

00:39:34.615 --> 00:39:37.885
I just hope that I'm wrong about this.

00:39:40.655 --> 00:39:41.825
Make sure you eat the porridge.

00:39:56.335 --> 00:39:58.835
(Boarding House)

00:40:09.455 --> 00:40:12.385
(Please keep quiet indoors.)

00:41:43.375 --> 00:41:46.385
It's safe here. Don't worry, and come on in.

00:41:58.025 --> 00:42:00.895
Remember what I told you on the way here.

00:42:01.295 --> 00:42:04.195
Everyone, keep outside contact to a minimum.

00:42:04.465 --> 00:42:07.165
And don't tell anyone you're here.

00:42:07.965 --> 00:42:09.575
Park Je Yeol is on the run,

00:42:09.835 --> 00:42:12.705
and we don't know what those users will try to pull.

00:42:12.875 --> 00:42:14.505
- Okay. - Right.

00:42:15.345 --> 00:42:17.245
I'll show you to your rooms. Follow me.

00:42:53.315 --> 00:42:54.315
Darn.

00:43:09.595 --> 00:43:12.595
There are two ways we can do this.

00:43:13.635 --> 00:43:14.665
First,

00:43:15.165 --> 00:43:17.705
we silence you for good.

00:43:20.245 --> 00:43:23.615
Second, we give you one last chance...

00:43:23.675 --> 00:43:25.345
to make up for all this.

00:43:27.315 --> 00:43:29.455
Which one would you prefer we choose?

00:43:30.755 --> 00:43:32.515
What are you trying to say?

00:43:34.025 --> 00:43:36.695
That I should take the fall for all of you...

00:43:37.355 --> 00:43:38.795
and go down alone?

00:43:39.425 --> 00:43:42.325
Either way, I'm the only one who gets screwed in the end.

00:43:44.265 --> 00:43:45.965
The deal doesn't add up.

00:43:46.765 --> 00:43:49.005
We'll make sure you won't be in prison for long.

00:43:51.175 --> 00:43:52.205
How long?

00:43:55.445 --> 00:43:58.845
Once this storm blows over, you'll be a free man.

00:44:00.215 --> 00:44:02.615
And we'll provide a hefty sum for your troubles.

00:44:19.465 --> 00:44:20.835
I'll be at Seoul Central District Prosecutors' Office...

00:44:21.365 --> 00:44:22.505
by 2pm.

00:44:25.935 --> 00:44:29.975
We're live. Prosecutor Park Je Yeol, a key Connect In case operator,

00:44:30.045 --> 00:44:32.845
has announced that he will voluntarily surrender himself...

00:44:32.915 --> 00:44:34.045
to the prosecution.

00:44:34.485 --> 00:44:36.415
Could you please comment on the current situation?

00:44:36.485 --> 00:44:37.985
Prosecutor, could we get a statement?

00:44:38.685 --> 00:44:40.885
(Prosecutors' Office)

00:44:44.555 --> 00:44:45.555
First of all,

00:44:46.125 --> 00:44:48.465
I sincerely apologise to the public...

00:44:49.195 --> 00:44:50.535
for causing so much concern.

00:44:52.735 --> 00:44:53.935
As for the Connect In app,

00:44:54.905 --> 00:44:57.375
I was the one who operated it.

00:44:58.705 --> 00:45:00.105
Are you admitting to all the charges?

00:45:00.345 --> 00:45:03.075
Is the VIP list claimed by LnJ authentic?

00:45:03.875 --> 00:45:06.115
I abused my position as a prosecutor...

00:45:06.985 --> 00:45:10.215
to make a mockery of the law and to profit improperly.

00:45:11.685 --> 00:45:15.525
To the victims irreparably harmed in the process,

00:45:15.725 --> 00:45:17.455
I have committed a grave sin.

00:45:18.595 --> 00:45:21.365
However, the list that LnJ released,

00:45:21.765 --> 00:45:24.195
the so-called "VIP list,"

00:45:24.935 --> 00:45:26.405
is completely false...

00:45:27.935 --> 00:45:29.065
What's going on?

00:45:29.465 --> 00:45:31.175
- What is this? - What?

00:45:31.875 --> 00:45:33.445
- What is this? - What?

00:45:33.675 --> 00:45:34.775
- What are they doing? - That's disgusting.

00:45:34.845 --> 00:45:35.845
Are they kissing?

00:45:36.475 --> 00:45:38.015
- What is that? - What's happening?

00:45:38.345 --> 00:45:40.415
These videos are being posted on social media right now.

00:45:40.945 --> 00:45:42.115
Care to explain?

00:45:43.785 --> 00:45:44.785
(Today's bombshell)

00:45:44.885 --> 00:45:46.885
Please help me.

00:45:47.325 --> 00:45:49.955
I was brought here against my will.

00:45:50.725 --> 00:45:52.795
- Please. - Darn it.

00:45:54.295 --> 00:45:56.535
- Give us a statement! - Prosecutor, are you running away?

00:45:56.595 --> 00:45:58.665
- Prosecutor, a statement! - Sir!

00:45:58.735 --> 00:46:01.135
- Prosecutor, wait! - Please explain!

00:46:01.205 --> 00:46:02.905
- Prosecutor! - Where are you going?

00:46:02.975 --> 00:46:04.605
- Was it all a lie? - Is it true?

00:46:04.675 --> 00:46:06.445
- Prosecutor! - What's going on?

00:46:06.705 --> 00:46:08.305
You said you'd turn yourself in. Why are you running away?

00:46:08.375 --> 00:46:09.575
Are you running away?

00:46:10.975 --> 00:46:12.145
Are you running away?

00:46:12.515 --> 00:46:13.515
Prosecutor!

00:46:16.985 --> 00:46:17.985
This is insane.

00:46:21.855 --> 00:46:22.885
What is this?

00:46:23.425 --> 00:46:24.425
Hey.

00:46:25.455 --> 00:46:26.825
Put more emotion into your voice.

00:46:27.665 --> 00:46:29.495
I told you, sound more desperate when you sob.

00:46:30.495 --> 00:46:31.995
That's more my taste.

00:46:32.495 --> 00:46:34.965
Ye Ji, did you see the videos they posted?

00:46:35.535 --> 00:46:37.305
You can see all the victims' faces.

00:46:37.675 --> 00:46:39.104
- Report it and take it down... - Everyone, come on out.

00:46:39.105 --> 00:46:40.804
- as fast as you can. - Turn off your phones...

00:46:40.805 --> 00:46:42.075
and stay off the internet.

00:46:46.885 --> 00:46:47.885
Attorney Yoon.

00:46:57.955 --> 00:47:01.265
(Connect In Evidence Video four)

00:47:02.995 --> 00:47:05.195
You think that's all I have on you?

00:47:05.665 --> 00:47:07.265
You're the one who escalated this, not me.

00:47:08.005 --> 00:47:09.065
That little jerk.

00:47:10.335 --> 00:47:11.505
(Park Je Yeol, Mujin District Prosecutor)

00:47:13.105 --> 00:47:14.745
(Park Je Yeol, Mujin District Prosecutor)

00:47:16.675 --> 00:47:19.574
- You dare screw me over like this? - It wasn't me.

00:47:19.575 --> 00:47:21.015
I also have no idea.

00:47:21.585 --> 00:47:23.415
I have no idea how any of this happened.

00:47:23.755 --> 00:47:26.115
All these videos were shot on our phones.

00:47:27.055 --> 00:47:29.455
If you didn't tamper with our phones then who did?

00:47:29.855 --> 00:47:32.755
Who else could've secretly filmed and leaked this trash?

00:47:33.125 --> 00:47:34.225
I'll find out who did it.

00:47:34.895 --> 00:47:38.035
I'll quickly find out who did this and why...

00:47:38.095 --> 00:47:39.095
Shut it.

00:47:39.665 --> 00:47:41.865
I'm about to teach you what a fate worse than death...

00:47:43.275 --> 00:47:44.335
really is.

00:48:36.555 --> 00:48:38.025
I just don't understand.

00:48:38.555 --> 00:48:39.555
This makes no sense.

00:48:40.295 --> 00:48:42.265
If Park Je Yeol didn't post it, who did?

00:48:42.765 --> 00:48:46.035
Think about it. Why would he suddenly surrender?

00:48:46.765 --> 00:48:48.835
He must've gotten his story straight with the other assailants.

00:48:51.435 --> 00:48:54.475
But did you see it? How he panicked when he saw the video?

00:48:55.545 --> 00:48:57.645
You think that cunning jerk would just throw away...

00:48:57.875 --> 00:48:59.785
his only lifeline like that?

00:49:13.565 --> 00:49:14.565
Attorney...

00:49:15.365 --> 00:49:16.365
We...

00:49:17.265 --> 00:49:18.795
can't do this anymore.

00:49:21.065 --> 00:49:23.375
- Su Eun. - Our voices,

00:49:23.735 --> 00:49:25.475
the brief glimpses of our faces...

00:49:25.775 --> 00:49:27.705
People are already going crazy online...

00:49:28.445 --> 00:49:30.545
trying to identify us.

00:49:31.415 --> 00:49:34.144
We'll do whatever we can to stop secondary harm.

00:49:34.145 --> 00:49:35.185
All we wanted...

00:49:36.115 --> 00:49:38.885
was to go back to our normal lives.

00:49:40.085 --> 00:49:44.525
We believed punishing those men was the only way we could.

00:49:46.095 --> 00:49:48.595
But now, it feels like it was all for nothing.

00:49:52.295 --> 00:49:54.635
Just releasing that one audio file...

00:49:55.135 --> 00:49:56.905
took us two sleepless nights.

00:49:58.205 --> 00:49:59.235
But...

00:50:00.175 --> 00:50:02.905
the whole world has seen it, Attorney.

00:50:03.575 --> 00:50:05.375
What they did to us.

00:50:11.715 --> 00:50:12.715
All right.

00:50:14.025 --> 00:50:15.225
I'll give you all a ride.

00:50:16.055 --> 00:50:19.395
But you have to pick up when I call, at least once a day.

00:50:19.655 --> 00:50:21.165
If you don't, I'm coming to hunt you down.

00:50:23.495 --> 00:50:26.805
And don't forget. You're always welcome here.

00:50:30.475 --> 00:50:32.875
I'll start the car. Grab your things and come on out.

00:50:43.855 --> 00:50:45.015
Where's that wench?

00:50:47.025 --> 00:50:49.895
That wench. Where is that crazy wench?

00:50:53.925 --> 00:50:54.925
What's going on?

00:50:57.365 --> 00:50:59.905
- What are you talking about? - Han Min Seo, that wench.

00:51:00.505 --> 00:51:02.035
You're hiding her, aren't you?

00:51:02.735 --> 00:51:04.435
She told me everything herself.

00:51:10.475 --> 00:51:12.315
Recognise me?

00:51:12.875 --> 00:51:15.845
Those brass knuckles. You're going to regret all of this.

00:51:16.385 --> 00:51:18.955
You're going to regret everything you've ever done.

00:51:19.155 --> 00:51:20.325
Even the day you were born.

00:51:21.355 --> 00:51:22.525
Even the day you were born.

00:51:24.525 --> 00:51:25.525
You...

00:51:27.365 --> 00:51:29.725
Those videos? I'm the one who posted them.

00:51:31.065 --> 00:51:32.465
I bet you're wondering how.

00:51:33.095 --> 00:51:34.205
Where are you right now?

00:51:34.635 --> 00:51:36.235
If you want to know, come and find me.

00:51:37.205 --> 00:51:38.305
I'll send you my location.

00:51:42.205 --> 00:51:43.375
What do you mean?

00:51:45.875 --> 00:51:49.615
Han Min Seo was the one who posted the videos? Not you?

00:51:50.055 --> 00:51:51.715
I didn't even know the darn thing existed.

00:51:52.255 --> 00:51:53.755
So, where is that wench?

00:51:54.285 --> 00:51:55.525
Where is she?

00:51:57.325 --> 00:51:59.625
Oh, right.

00:52:00.195 --> 00:52:02.195
You're all here together.

00:52:02.995 --> 00:52:05.735
Perfect. Now I can take you all out at once.

00:52:08.465 --> 00:52:10.275
Is he here for us?

00:52:10.335 --> 00:52:12.675
Call the police, now. I'll get them inside.

00:52:16.475 --> 00:52:17.815
You put her up to this, didn't you?

00:52:18.245 --> 00:52:21.045
Trying to get revenge on me? Is that it?

00:52:22.745 --> 00:52:24.655
You put her up to it, right?

00:52:26.985 --> 00:52:30.125
I knew something was off. That's it.

00:52:30.555 --> 00:52:31.955
It was a trap.

00:52:32.295 --> 00:52:34.525
This was all a setup from the start, wasn't it?

00:52:35.125 --> 00:52:36.125
Right?

00:52:43.605 --> 00:52:46.845
This piece of trash still doesn't get it.

00:52:47.005 --> 00:52:49.975
Yes. You were there too, right?

00:52:58.385 --> 00:53:00.055
You ruined everything.

00:53:00.855 --> 00:53:01.855
You hear me?

00:53:03.325 --> 00:53:06.965
You wenches ruined everything! You hear me?

00:53:09.695 --> 00:53:10.695
I'll end this.

00:55:01.575 --> 00:55:05.215
Someone's been hurt.

00:55:17.725 --> 00:55:18.725
(Attorney Yoon Ra Young)

00:55:18.795 --> 00:55:20.095
(Thank you...)

00:55:24.165 --> 00:55:25.465
Thank you, Mom,

00:55:26.195 --> 00:55:27.435
for killing Dad.

00:55:54.395 --> 00:55:58.395
The safest way to dispose of a bomb that's served its purpose...

00:56:07.145 --> 00:56:09.205
is to just go ahead and pull the pin.

00:56:18.385 --> 00:56:19.955
(CEO Baek Tae Joo)

00:56:20.015 --> 00:56:21.325
(The Prime)

00:56:27.865 --> 00:56:29.365
It's infested.

00:56:29.795 --> 00:56:32.535
If I leave it, it will contaminate the whole thing.

00:56:33.465 --> 00:56:34.835
So, you use pesticides?

00:56:35.705 --> 00:56:38.535
Rather than that, I lure them with the trap pests like.

00:56:40.375 --> 00:56:41.445
The pests...

00:56:41.845 --> 00:56:44.015
take the bait without ever knowing it's a trap.

00:57:08.665 --> 00:57:12.635
(Honour)

00:58:04.255 --> 00:58:05.495
I won't say rest in peace.

00:58:05.895 --> 00:58:08.925
- You're in the fiery pit anyway. - Find Han Min Seo.

00:58:09.195 --> 00:58:12.065
She's the one who lured Park Je Yeol to the villa too.

00:58:12.495 --> 00:58:13.495
I'm sorry.

00:58:14.365 --> 00:58:16.035
This has gone on long enough.

00:58:16.605 --> 00:58:18.175
Stop Ra Young from being released.

00:58:18.375 --> 00:58:20.875
We can't prove self-defence without eyewitness testimony.

00:58:21.245 --> 00:58:25.175
You just ruined my whole life, Mom!

00:58:26.075 --> 00:58:27.515
I have to get out of here.

00:58:28.145 --> 00:58:30.455
There's someone behind Min Seo.